Our logo is a variation of a Celtic knot. Why a Celtic knot? Because a Celtic knot derives its strength from its other parts. And if you stress a Celtic knot by pulling on one side, the knot only gets stronger.

Like the Celtic knot, Plexus derives its strength from its relationships. In times of uncertainty, we rely on the more than 15 years of experience investing successfully as a team.

We are patient investors providing access to the experience it takes to succeed.

Plexus Capital. The access you want. The patience you need.









