Overview

Plexus Capital and Mezzanine Investing from Border Row Productions on Vimeo.
 
Plexus Capital focuses on investments and partnerships with middle market businesses that need capital for growth.  Whether the need for capital is driven by new market opportunities, a transition of ownership or strategic acquisitions, the Plexus team has the capital and experience you need.
 
After raising $950 million across four funds, completing investments in more than 80 businesses, and successfully managing through all economic cycles, we have proven ourselves to be patient investors with the experience it takes to succeed.















