How to submit your investment opportunity:
Please email your business plan to either Robert Gefaell or Mike Becker, or if you prefer, send a hard copy to Robert Gefaell at the Charlotte office address listed above or to Mike Becker at the Raleigh office address above. We welcome the opportunity to review your business plan and will respond to your investment opportunity as soon as possible.
















